  "title": "Single-pulse open-loop TMS-EEG dataset",
  "description": "A single-pulse transcranial magnetic stimulation (TMS) combined with electroencephalography (EEG) dataset acquired in open-loop configuration. This dataset provides concurrent TMS-EEG recordings suitable for investigating cortical responses to magnetic stimulation and characterizing brain reactivity to non-invasive neuromodulation. The dataset comprises recordings from multiple subjects across multiple sessions with concurrent TMS-EEG acquisition.",
